Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.15,0:02:41.97,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}だからそう Fight back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.97,0:02:44.07,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Ay yo stand up, over and over
